## Database Diagrams

### ERD General — NutriSense (todos los bounded contexts)

El diagrama presenta las 11 tablas principales del sistema y sus relaciones. Las tablas se agrupan según su bounded context:

| Bounded Context | Tablas |
|---|---|
| Identity & Access Management | `user_accounts` |
| Nutrition Tracking | `consumption_logs`, `food_entries` |
| Body & Health Metrics | `health_profiles`, `weight_records` |
| Smart Recommendations | `recommendation_sets`, `food_recommendations` |
| Activity & Wearable Sync | `activity_sync_sessions`, `activity_records` |
| Analytics & Reporting | `progress_insights` |
| Subscriptions & Billing | `subscriptions` |

```plantuml
@startuml NutriSense - ERD General (PostgreSQL)

!define PK <b><color:DarkBlue>PK</color></b>
!define FK <color:DarkGreen>FK</color>
!define UK <i><color:DarkOrange>UK</color></i>

skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor #FAFAF6
skinparam ClassBorderColor #C0BDB4
