### Descripción de constraints por tabla

**`user_accounts`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `UNIQUE (email)`
- `CHECK (role IN ('free_user', 'premium_user', 'admin'))`
- `NOT NULL` en todos los campos excepto nada (todos requeridos)

**`consumption_logs`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_accounts(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `UNIQUE (user_id, log_date)` — un usuario tiene máximo un log por día

**`food_entries`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (consumption_log_id) REFERENCES consumption_logs(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `CHECK (amount > 0)`
- `CHECK (calories >= 0)`
- `CHECK (external_food_source IN ('open_food_facts', 'usda'))`

**`health_profiles`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_accounts(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `UNIQUE (user_id)` — un usuario tiene exactamente un perfil de salud
- `CHECK (height_cm > 0)`
- `CHECK (health_goal IN ('lose_weight', 'gain_muscle', 'maintain'))`
- `CHECK (activity_level IN ('sedentary', 'lightly_active', 'moderately_active', 'very_active', 'extra_active'))`

**`weight_records`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (health_profile_id) REFERENCES health_profiles(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `CHECK (weight_kg > 0)`

**`recommendation_sets`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_accounts(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `CHECK (weather_condition IN ('hot', 'cold', 'rainy', 'neutral'))`
- `CHECK (time_of_day IN ('breakfast', 'lunch', 'dinner', 'snack'))`

**`food_recommendations`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (recommendation_set_id) REFERENCES recommendation_sets(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `CHECK (match_score BETWEEN 0.0 AND 1.0)`

**`activity_sync_sessions`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_accounts(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `CHECK (provider IN ('google_fit', 'manual'))`
- `CHECK (status IN ('pending', 'in_progress', 'completed', 'failed'))`
- `CHECK (period_end > period_start)`

**`activity_records`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES activity_sync_sessions(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `CHECK (duration_minutes > 0)`
- `CHECK (calories_burned >= 0)`
- `CHECK (activity_type IN ('walking', 'running', 'cycling', 'swimming', 'strength', 'other'))`

**`progress_insights`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_accounts(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `CHECK (period_to >= period_from)`
- `CHECK (period_type IN ('weekly', 'monthly', 'custom'))`
- `CHECK (avg_protein_pct + avg_carbs_pct + avg_fat_pct BETWEEN 99.0 AND 101.0)`
- `CHECK (goal_adherence_pct BETWEEN 0.0 AND 100.0)`

**`subscriptions`**
- `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- `FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_accounts(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`
- `UNIQUE (user_id)` — un usuario tiene máximo una suscripción activa
- `CHECK (plan_type IN ('free', 'premium', 'premium_annual'))`
- `CHECK (status IN ('active', 'cancelled', 'past_due', 'trialing'))`
- `CHECK (billing_period_end > billing_period_start)`